So you have societal challenges,
you have industrial leadership,

00:33:54.800 --> 00:33:58.530
and you have research excellence.

00:33:58.530 --> 00:34:02.710
We just talked about the
leadership opportunities.

00:34:02.710 --> 00:34:05.280
Now we look at the
societal challenges.

