So therefore, it's really
quite a broad panoply

00:36:01.370 --> 00:36:06.110
of topics that are-- that come up.

00:36:06.110 --> 00:36:10.450
So I say, the 2017 work
program has a number

00:36:10.450 --> 00:36:15.080
of specific culture heritage
research opportunities.

00:36:15.080 --> 00:36:19.820
But it's not only inclusive
on reflective societies,

00:36:19.820 --> 00:36:25.160
the six cultural-- the
six societal challenge,

00:36:25.160 --> 00:36:26.810
where opportunities exist.

