become a full participant,

00:54:03.300 --> 00:54:08.380
that is to be in the project
proposal from the very beginning,

00:54:08.380 --> 00:54:11.610
have the proposal selected and
to sign the grant agreement,

00:54:11.610 --> 00:54:15.380
even if you're not getting funding.

00:54:15.380 --> 00:54:18.320
So, it always sounds funny that
you've signed the grant agreement

00:54:18.320 --> 00:54:19.720
without getting any funding.

00:54:19.720 --> 00:54:22.380
But the grant agreement
is, I suppose, only a term

00:54:22.380 --> 00:54:23.990
but it's the contract that we have

00:54:23.990 --> 00:54:26.930
that the research we're
funding will be carried out.

00:54:26.930 --> 00:54:31.060 position:56%
So this is the most basic way and
the most common way of participating

00:54:31.060 --> 00:54:35.110
in Horizon 2020 project for
an American institution.

00:54:35.110 --> 00:54:39.310
And there's also a
possibility to participate

00:54:39.310 --> 00:54:42.020
as what we call a third party.

00:54:42.020 --> 00:54:47.440
