00:54:56.130 --> 00:54:58.490
So in a way, it's a little
bit like a subcontract

00:54:58.490 --> 00:55:03.020
that an American partner will
get but strongly linked to one

00:55:03.020 --> 00:55:04.480
of the European partners.

00:55:04.480 --> 00:55:08.010
