we cannot sign the grant agreement

00:55:51.090 --> 00:55:54.220
because the grant agreement is--

00:55:55.530 --> 00:55:57.620
because we're not receiving
any funding.

00:55:57.620 --> 00:56:01.710
The grant agreement is too heavy
a document for us to sign as to.

00:56:01.710 --> 00:56:05.610
It commits us to too
many legal commitments.

00:56:05.610 --> 00:56:07.910
This is only in some cases.

00:56:07.910 --> 00:56:11.480
Many university sign without
any problem because they don't--

00:56:11.480 --> 00:56:13.310
they just don't have that problem.

00:56:13.310 --> 00:56:18.460
So therefore, in order
to relieve that problem,

00:56:18.460 --> 00:56:21.400
the United States Department
of State

00:56:21.400 --> 00:56:26.150
and the European Commission
worked on finding a solution.

00:56:26.150 --> 00:56:29.040
And the work to find the
solution took a long time.

00:56:29.040 --> 00:56:33.320
The solution itself is
supremely simple and elegant,

00:56:33.320 --> 00:56:37.110
and it simply means that
the European project

00:56:37.110 --> 00:56:41.560
and the American partner
can simply--

00:56:41.560 --> 00:56:43.620
once the European has
the European funding

00:56:43.620 --> 00:56:45.870
and once the American
has the American funding,

00:56:45.870 --> 00:56:48.260
they can collaborate together
without anybody having

00:56:48.260 --> 00:56:50.330
to sign anybody else's
grant agreement.

00:56:50.330 --> 00:56:54.350
So therefore, what it basically
means is that the European project,

00:56:54.350 --> 00:56:58.250
Horizon 2020, even if it knows
from the beginning that it's going

00:56:58.250 --> 00:57:01.720
to have-- that is going to work
together with an American partner,

00:57:01.720 --> 00:57:06.130
doesn't even have to
mention the American entity

00:57:06.130 --> 00:57:08.510
in the research proposal.

00:57:08.510 --> 00:57:12.930
The American partner likewise,
you know, request its own funding

00:57:12.930 --> 00:57:15.350
from its own national
funding mechanism.

00:57:15.350 --> 00:57:16.790
And only at the end,
they come together

00:57:16.790 --> 00:57:20.720
and they decide themselves the
extent of their collaboration

00:57:20.720 --> 00:57:24.390
and they decide amongst themselves
the extent of the sharing

00:57:24.390 --> 00:57:27.260
of resources, the sharing
of knowledge.

00:57:27.260 --> 00:57:30.740
And this was considered to be the
easiest because those who want

00:57:30.740 --> 00:57:33.580
to collaborate very deeply
can collaborate very deeply.

00:57:33.580 --> 00:57:37.390
It's entirely up to
the funded projects.

00:57:37.390 --> 00:57:42.190
And those who want only a
lighter form of cooperation maybe

00:57:42.190 --> 00:57:45.050
within occasional workshop together
