years ago, more than 15.

01:04:46.820 --> 01:04:50.810 position:56%
When we started the collaboration to
European level in cultural heritage,

01:04:50.810 --> 01:04:54.550
this is the stream of projects
that have been financed

01:04:54.550 --> 01:04:58.030
by the European Commission,
trying to integrate

01:04:58.030 --> 01:05:00.960
