01:05:50.120 --> 01:05:53.110
The project is an integrating
activity

01:05:53.110 --> 01:05:55.850
that is the technical
name in Europe.

01:05:55.850 --> 01:06:00.740
The grant is 8 million and we
are now approaching the midterm.

01:06:00.740 --> 01:06:04.980
