And then here is the landscape,
is what is currently going

01:11:17.160 --> 01:11:19.620
on in infrastructure at ESFRI level

01:11:19.620 --> 01:11:22.440
in the social and cultural
innovation.

01:11:22.440 --> 01:11:25.130
It explains graphically
what Riccardo was saying.

