the E-RIHS was included

01:12:17.210 --> 01:12:22.790
in the new strategic roadmap of
research infrastructures in Europe.

01:12:22.790 --> 01:12:25.990
And this is the actual
roadmap already discussed.

01:12:25.990 --> 01:12:32.010
