it has became not anymore an

01:12:32.010 --> 01:12:35.790
integrating activity but
actually a strategic project

01:12:35.790 --> 01:12:38.530
of the European Union.

01:12:38.530 --> 01:12:42.640
I don't want to discuss because
we don't have enough time,

01:12:42.640 --> 01:12:44.800
what is heritage science.

01:12:44.800 --> 01:12:48.670
Heritage science concept
is open to discussion.

01:12:48.670 --> 01:12:53.840
Very briefly and my mind
is making signs together.

01:12:53.840 --> 01:12:56.740
So not anymore science
for conservation,

01:12:56.740 --> 01:13:00.020
not anymore users our museums.

01:13:00.020 --> 01:13:03.110
No, we are all there
together to do science

01:13:03.110 --> 01:13:04.660
for the heritage preservation.

01:13:04.660 --> 01:13:09.780
That is my concept in general
lines, where general lines.

01:13:09.780 --> 01:13:13.470 position:56%
And so we define this
infrastructure with the specific aim

01:13:13.470 --> 01:13:16.110
to support the heritage
science community.

01:13:16.110 --> 01:13:20.870
And I must say that probably the
infrastructure will be first.

01:13:20.870 --> 01:13:23.680
And then the heritage
science community,

01:13:23.680 --> 01:13:28.050
because we are still discussing
in several countries about how

01:13:28.050 --> 01:13:34.380 position:56%
to define the real borders, the real
extension of what we have in mind.

01:13:34.380 --> 01:13:37.770
And we need to know that because
we need to organize the services

01:13:37.770 --> 01:13:40.620
of the big infrastructure covering
the needs of heritage science.

01:13:40.620 --> 01:13:44.560
So some exercise of analysis
and strategic planning

01:13:44.560 --> 01:13:47.150
